0.9.0.name: aedart/model-uuid
0.9.0.description: Getter and Setter package for Universally unique identifier (UUID). This package is part of the 'Aedart\Model' namespace; visit https://bitbucket.org/aedart/model to learn more about the project. Official sub-package website (https://bitbucket.org/aedart/model-uuid).

suggest.aedart\/overload: Provides means to dynamically deal with inaccessible properties, by implementing PHP’s magic methods; __get(), __set(), __isset(), and __unset().
